detaileddescription.para: The PP2_VM macro invokes the PP2 virtual machine, executing the instruction specified by insn with the VM registers initialized to the contents of acc, stack, and heap.

parameterdescription.para: the contents of the VM accumulator register
the contents of the VM local context register
the contents of the VM global context register
the name of the first instruction to be executed by the VM
the arguments to the first instruction, and all remaining instructions and instruction arguments to be executed

simplesect.para: the Sequence of tokens emitted during execution
